{"id":"284787866_Remark_on_a_Result_of_Constantine","abstract":"In this short note we construct codes of length $4n$ with $8n+8$ codewords\nand minimum distance $2n-2$ whenever $4n+4$ is the order of a Hadamard matrix.\nThis generalises work of Constantine who obtained a similar result in the\nspecial case that $n$ is a prime power.","authors":["Padraig Ó Catháin"],"meta":["March 2018Annals of Combinatorics 22(3)","DOI:10.1007/s00026-018-0379-z","SourcearXiv"],"references":["302222704_On_orthogonal_matrices","285945919_Hadamard_Matrices_and_their_Applications","284035746_Thoughts_on_inverse_orthogonal_matrices_simultaneous_sign-_successions_and_tessellated_pavements_in_two_or_more_colors_with_applications_to_Newton's_rule_ornamental_tile-work_and_the_theory_of_numbers","277888325_An_Alternative_to_Hadamard_Codes_-_One_Error_for_the_Price_of_Existence","268854192_On_the_products_of_Hadamard_matrices_Williamson_matrices_and_other_orthogonal_matrices_using_M-structures","268683218_Error-Correcting_Codes","268616197_Resolution_d'une_question_relative_aux_derminants","268247580_Hadamard_matrices_sequences_and_block_designs","267023028_Algebraic_Design_Theory","265897660_Hadamard_Matrices_and_Their_Applications","265681394_A_Family_of_Difference_Sets","235410288_Error_Correcting_Codes","233331698_LX_Thoughts_on_inverse_orthogonal_matrices_simultaneous_signsuccessions_and_tessellated_pavements_in_two_or_more_colours_with_applications_to_Newton's_rule_ornamental_tile-work_and_the_theory_of_numbe","227600680_On_the_Classification_of_Hadamard_Matrices_of_Order_32","226680798_On_a_new_class_of_Hadamard_determinants"]}